    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/korean-skincare-uk/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=555231466183722084&sectionId=559501774780629801)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7A8_qKcNf_text","label":"gg7A8_qKcNf_text","default":"<p>Fair folks, the 5th edition of the Korean Skincare Hunt, The Glow White Hunt,<strong> has now ended!</strong><br>Glow White &amp; the KS Team thank you from the bottom of our hearts for participating! We hope your Hunt was successful and filled with discounts &amp; free gifts. To satisfy your curiosity, let us reveal the secret <strong>hints </strong>we had scattered everywhere, as well as the <strong>location </strong>of our most-coveted discounts.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQpAGA8BVt_text","label":"ggQpAGA8BVt_text","default":"<p>During the hunt, you could find these elixirs:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjlOsRn4zU_text","label":"ggjlOsRn4zU_text","default":"<p>10%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2qzrmEzqO_text","label":"gg2qzrmEzqO_text","default":"<p><strong>15 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which could be used a total of 500 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfNwCw3xgx_text","label":"ggfNwCw3xgx_text","default":"<p>20%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd8KrvbUMQ_text","label":"ggd8KrvbUMQ_text","default":"<p><strong>10 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which could be used a total of 300 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHDOgbtbs5_text","label":"ggHDOgbtbs5_text","default":"<p>30%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRzR1cHZWh_text","label":"ggRzR1cHZWh_text","default":"<p><strong>5 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which could be used a total of 60 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJ0_Cm-LZA_text","label":"ggJ0_Cm-LZA_text","default":"<p>50%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKWEvt4_uU_text","label":"ggKWEvt4_uU_text","default":"<p><strong>2 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which could be used a total of 6 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdHRmFnyyx_text","label":"ggdHRmFnyyx_text","default":"<p><a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/melixir-vegan-lip-butter?variant=50789635916125\" target=\"_blank\">Free product</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLgPgQTQs1_text","label":"ggLgPgQTQs1_text","default":"<p><strong>10 different codes</strong>&nbsp;<br>which could be used a total of 30 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_ruOHESaz_childItem_0","label":"gg_ruOHESaz_childItem_0","default":"<p>Hints: Glow White&#039;s tale</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4jnIBWEIb_text","label":"gg4jnIBWEIb_text","default":"<p><i>Glow White's Tale was filled with clues as to where the elixirs are hidden...</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggm_LedtXyK_text","label":"ggm_LedtXyK_text","default":"<p>Once upon a time there lived a princess, with glowing skin white as <strong>milk</strong>, hair <strong>black </strong>as ebony and <strong>blood</strong>-red lips, and her name was Glow White. The Evil Queen that had replaced her beloved <strong>mother </strong>was cruel and envied her <strong>pure glow</strong>, as she sought to keep youth and beauty to herself with her elixirs.<br><br>Shaken to her <strong>core </strong>by the Evil Queen's cruelty, Glow White put on her red <strong>velvet </strong>cloak and fled the castle she once called home without saying <strong>good bye</strong>.<br><br>As she wandered through the <strong>mossy </strong>trees, the <strong>spring </strong>sun warmed the earth and the air was filled with the scent of <strong>peach blossoms</strong>. She picked a <strong>red flower</strong>, and birds fluttered close, so she fed them the <strong>bean seeds</strong> she kept in her pocket.<br><br>Lost but unafraid, she stumbled upon a charming cottage nestled beside a thriving <strong>pumpkin </strong>patch. The <strong>door opened</strong> to welcome her, and within she found the most <strong>loyal </strong>friends. In their care, she learned that the <strong>miracle light</strong> of kindness could shine even in the darkest of shadows.<br><br>But the Queen’s jealousy was relentless, she could not stand that the elixirs that made her glow were shared with the kingdom, their magic no longer hers alone. Disguised, she came bearing a poisoned gift. One bite, and Glow White fell into an enchanted slumber, until a prince’s gentle kiss <strong>awakened </strong>her.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0KK7ZZG4V_text","label":"gg0KK7ZZG4V_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><i>TirTir - <strong>Milk </strong>Skin Toner</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaNXZ48cqI_text","label":"ggaNXZ48cqI_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><i>Pyunkang Yul - <strong>Black </strong>Tea Time Reverse Eye Patch</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvuCaFYE5q_text","label":"ggvuCaFYE5q_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><i>Skin1004 - <strong>Bloody </strong>Peel Light</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZhU4fGkWq_text","label":"ggZhU4fGkWq_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><i>SkinTalks - Gift Ideas: For <strong>Mother'</strong>s Day</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2YWYpSReQ_text","label":"gg2YWYpSReQ_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><i>SOME BY MI - Galactomyces <strong>Pure</strong> Vitamin C <strong>Glow </strong>Toner</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBp9BZj1pk_text","label":"ggBp9BZj1pk_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><i>Hamel - Double Shot 12GF <strong>Core </strong>Glow Mist Serum</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTQA4Lb6Td_text","label":"ggTQA4Lb6Td_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><i>Numbuzin - No.3 <strong>Velvet </strong>Beauty Cream</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWRZhutbkF_text","